WEBVTT

1
01:24:56.610 --> 01:24:58.900 
在他卖给我和艾莫斯家具的时候
When he sold Amos and me our furniture.

2
01:24:59.120 --> 01:25:01.120 
那你和他的私人关系呢
Your personal relationship with him,

3
01:25:01.200 --> 01:25:02.320 
你能告诉陪审团是从什么时候开始的吗
you tell the jury when that began.

4
01:25:02.770 --> 01:25:05.830 
从有一天晚上我让他送我回家开始的
When l permitted him to escort me home one night,

5
01:25:06.120 --> 01:25:07.840 
我想我不会和他一起的
l don't think l would've gone with him

6
01:25:07.860 --> 01:25:10.700 
如果哈特那天早晨没和我吵架
If Mr. Hart and me hadn't quarreled that very morning.

7
01:25:10.940 --> 01:25:11.400 
吵架了
Quarreled?

8
01:25:11.560 --> 01:25:12.340 
是的 先生
Yes, sir.

9
01:25:12.400 --> 01:25:13.080 
好的 我
Well, l

10
01:25:13.340 --> 01:25:14.620 
假设是他的错
supposed it was his fault.

11
01:25:14.920 --> 01:25:17.330 
哦 不 先生 是我的错
Oh, no, sir. lt was my fault.

12
01:25:17.630 --> 01:25:20.420 
我觉得是因为我不停的埋怨他
l supposed l just couldn't stop pestering him.

13
01:25:20.710 --> 01:25:22.130 
埋怨他 为什么呢
Pestering him? About what?

14
01:25:22.340 --> 01:25:25.300 
我不喜欢他在修车厂每天工作那么多时间
l didn't like him working those long hours at the garage.

15
01:25:25.320 --> 01:25:27.080 
我想他在家里陪着我
l wanted him home with me...

